MAP BOOK (mapbook.hts)
hypertext
{
<tab><cl=F0F010>MAP BOOK<cl=A2A2A2><br><br>
<tab>You keep all your maps in this book. To open a map, just double-click its name using the left mouse button.<br>
<tab>The "M" key (default key) opens the map of the location where you are now. If there are several such maps, the one at the top of the list opens.<br>
} 